      "date": "2019-11-22 19:47:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nHi Shaun, I built current lustre-master against both zfs-0.7 and zfs-master and it correctly detected multihost and built without errors.  I do not see what needs to be fixed.  Can you give the specific symptoms you are seeing and the software versions?  Thanks.",
